                  <span class="service-card__link">
                    Learn more
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                  </span>
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>

            <div class="carousel-slide">
              <a href="/services#pain" class="service-card">
                <div class="service-card__icon-wrap">
                  <div class="service-card__icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/></svg>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card__content">
                  <h3 class="service-card__title">Pain Management</h3>
                  <p class="service-card__text">Comprehensive approach to managing chronic and acute pain without medications.</p>
                  <span class="service-card__link">
                    Learn more
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                  </span>
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>

            <div class="carousel-slide">
              <a href="/services#wellness" class="service-card">
                <div class="service-card__icon-wrap">
                  <div class="service-card__icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card__content">
                  <h3 class="service-card__title">Wellness Care</h3>
                  <p class="service-card__text">Ongoing maintenance care to keep you feeling your best and prevent future issues.</p>
                  <span class="service-card__link">
                    Learn more
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                  </span>
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button class="carousel-arrow carousel-arrow--next" id="carousel-next" aria-label="Next slide">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>
        </button>

        <div class="carousel-dots" id="carousel-dots"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section class="section section--gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-image">
          <img src="/images/IMG_0954.JPG" alt="Dr. Nathan Beyerl" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-content">
          <h2>Your Trusted Chiropractic Care Experts</h2>
          <p>Dr. Nathan Beyerl brings over 15 years of experience to every patient interaction. With a focus on movement-based care, he helps adults in San Diego stay active and independent.</p>

          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Personalized treatment plans for every patient</li>
            <li>Education-first approach to lasting results</li>
            <li>Specializing in adults 55 and older</li>
            <li>Fall prevention & balance training for seniors</li>
            <li>Gentle techniques for all comfort levels</li>
          </ul>

          <a href="/about" class="btn btn--primary">Meet Dr. Beyerl</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

