  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="faq-layout">
        <div class="faq-header">
          <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          <p>Have questions about chiropractic care? We've got answers.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Ask a Question</a>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-item__question" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>What should I expect during my first visit?</span>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-item__answer">
              <p>Your first visit includes a comprehensive consultation, examination, and discussion of your health history. We'll take the time to understand your concerns and create a personalized treatment plan. Expect to spend about 45-60 minutes with us.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-item__question" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Is chiropractic care safe?</span>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-item__answer">
              <p>Yes, chiropractic care is very safe when performed by a licensed professional. Dr. Beyerl uses gentle techniques and adjusts his approach based on each patient's comfort level and health needs.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-item__question" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>How many visits will I need?</span>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-item__answer">
              <p>The number of visits varies based on your condition and goals. Some patients feel relief after just a few visits, while others benefit from ongoing wellness care. We'll discuss a recommended treatment plan during your first visit.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-item__question" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Do you accept insurance?</span>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-item__answer">
              <p>We accept most major insurance plans and can help you understand your coverage. Contact our office for specific information about your insurance plan.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Book Your Appointment Now</h2>
